I fixed a small bug in the script that makes the squirrels chitter. They
no longer chitter when other squirrels enter the room. As before, they
don't pester the novice or accepted mobs, either. They still chitter when
a player enters the room, though. But, unless someone is running back and
forth, they should no longer spam RP, since their own wanderings do not
cause spam.
